To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Tristar _tristar;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_tristar = Tristar(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_tristar.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "tristar", _tristar.Current.Value);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.tristar = self.Tristar(symbol)

# In OnData()
if self.tristar.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "tristar", self.tristar.Current.Value)
